Package team1.model

Interface ElecComponent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Capacitor, Inductor, Resistor
    public interface ElecComponent
    This interface contains the main methods to describes a electrical component (R, L, C) with its parasitic parameters. Additionally it contains a method to calculate the impedance of the electrical component
